text: Mohammad Ali ( â€“ 13 November 2020) was a Bangladeshi politician. He was a Member of Parliament of Cox's Bazar-4 from 1996 to 2001. Ali was a member of the Awami League. Ali died on 13 November 2020 at a hospital in Cox's Bazar, Bangladesh at the age of 76. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Politicians from Chittagong Division Category:7th Jatiya Sangsad members
